  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, not together, after that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "First my mother and my brother were arrested, then I a few hours later.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Yeah, I can describe that, because there were two SS [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] officers coming up to our apartment.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They drove a Red Cross car, a giant red cross on top of the car-- making sure that they wouldn't be bombed-- and drove me to the-- to the prison, [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] where we kept our clothes.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "In fact, we could call to get a toothbrush or whatever [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] sent.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "See, I didn't tell you this, but the same lady who-- who ran the one-room-- the pension in which we had one room later lived with us in one room, in our apartment.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And so they notified her.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Then we got a sweater and a toothbrush after some time.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Anyway, we were obviously put into a Jewish section of the prison.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "A cell that was probably made for two 2 3 people, now had 20, 25 people in it.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Very hard to breathe.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And-- and these were, most of them [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] Polish and Hungarian Orthodox Jews, with beards, with [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] the works, prayed in their own way a great deal, you know, moving their bodies, traditionally sort of singing.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Just men.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "There was just-- OK.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I should say I was taken into the same cell in which I found my brother.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So the two of us-- two of us were in this overcrowded cell.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And really, this was our first encounter of our lives with-- with people whose religion was Judaism [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] and their prayers and whatnot.",
      "word_count": 26
    }
  ],
